Best Worst Movie;;84;;94;;NC;;This documentary reviews the making of the film "Troll 2" from the perspective of its former child actor star, Michael Stephenson. In 1989, a group of actors and an Italian production crew join forces to produce a slice of unwitting cinematic history. Stephenson and those involved with the ill-fated sequel tell the story of Italian director Claudio Fragasso's B-movie classic, among them the Alabama dentist who became a cult star because of his famous, immortal line.;;Documentary;;Michael Stephenson;;2010;;George Hardy,Michael Stephenson,Darren Ewing,Jason Wright,Randall Colburn,Adam Deyoe,Patrick Gibbs,Paul Gibbs,Eric Gosselin,Timothy Marklevitz;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/best_worst_movie